Random Joke Generator

A simple Python application that fetches and displays random jokes from an online API. The application includes a graphical user interface (GUI) built using Tkinter, with features such as category selection, viewing previously seen jokes, and toggling dark mode.
Features

    --Fetch Random Jokes: Get a random joke from a broad category or a specific category.
    --Category Selection: Select from various joke categories to get jokes that fit your preference.
    --View Seen Jokes: Display all previously seen jokes in a separate window.
    --Reset Preferences: Reset all user preferences and seen jokes.
    --Dark Mode: Toggle between light and dark themes for the application interface.
